name: r-bootnet
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.5" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-bootnet
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/bootnet_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/bootnet/bootnet_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 118e35c3de19001508e9508a5678e9d358b9c8ef6890e4c79a33fa5444aeee8e

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic

  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-bdgraph
    - r-isingfit
    - r-isingsampler
    - r-matrix
    - r-networktoolbox >=1.1.0
    - r-abind
    - r-corpcor
    - r-dplyr >=0.3.0.2
    - r-ggplot2
    - r-glasso
    - r-graphicalvar
    - r-gtools
    - r-huge
    - r-igraph
    - r-lavaan
    - r-mgm >=1.2
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-networktools
    - r-pbapply
    - r-psychtools
    - r-qgraph
    - r-relaimpo
    - r-tidyr
    - r-snow

  run:
    - r-base
    - r-bdgraph
    - r-isingfit
    - r-isingsampler
    - r-matrix
    - r-networktoolbox >=1.1.0
    - r-abind
    - r-corpcor
    - r-dplyr >=0.3.0.2
    - r-ggplot2
    - r-glasso
    - r-graphicalvar
    - r-gtools
    - r-huge
    - r-igraph
    - r-lavaan
    - r-mgm >=1.2
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-networktools
    - r-pbapply
    - r-psychtools
    - r-qgraph
    - r-relaimpo
    - r-tidyr
    - r-snow

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('bootnet')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('bootnet')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=bootnet
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  summary: Bootstrap methods to assess accuracy and stability of estimated network structures and centrality indices <doi:10.3758/s13428-017-0862-1>. Allows for flexible specification of any undirected network estimation procedure in R, and offers default sets for various estimation routines.

  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - izahn
